        "mainbody": "'''Shira''' was a great black wolf, companion to [[Thanial Selwander]]. The first night that [[Marrec]] spent with them as Thanial's apprentice, she sniffed him suspiciously.{{cite book/Lady of Poison|59|7}} She participated in the fighting during the raid on the village by the [[Durang]] [[ogres]]. After Marrec accidentally petrified Thanial during the fight, she fled.{{cite book/Lady of Poison|114-116|13}}"
